1
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:06,480
Who is this handsome guy?

2
00:00:07,040 --> 00:00:08,080
Oh, no way!

3
00:00:10,280 --> 00:00:11,680
Watch out!

4
00:00:13,560 --> 00:00:15,280
Hey! Hurry up!

5
00:00:15,280 --> 00:00:17,040
We won't be ready in time!

6
00:00:17,400 --> 00:00:18,400
Hey!

7
00:00:21,760 --> 00:00:23,720
Where should we hang out after school? We can grab dinner before heading home.

8
00:00:25,480 --> 00:00:27,360
Sure. Is something wrong?

9
00:00:28,320 --> 00:00:30,200
I don't really want to go home.

10
00:00:32,160 --> 00:00:33,320
Did you get into a fight with your mom?

11
00:00:34,160 --> 00:00:35,560
It's not exactly a fight with my mom...

12
00:00:37,000 --> 00:00:38,000
Oh.

13
00:00:38,560 --> 00:00:40,200
Speak of the devil.

14
00:00:40,680 --> 00:00:41,560
Ah.

15
00:00:41,560 --> 00:00:43,120
Kono Mizuki.

16
00:00:47,080 --> 00:00:48,640
What a waste.

17
00:00:50,260 --> 00:00:51,860
No, that's not it at all.

18
00:00:52,300 --> 00:00:54,420
I can't believe a guy like that is my stepbrother.

19
00:00:54,420 --> 00:00:55,860
I just can't accept it.

20
00:00:56,860 --> 00:00:59,400
So much for my happy, peaceful life.

21
00:00:59,400 --> 00:01:01,560
Please go out with me.
